        "rich_text_KFEFt3": {
          "type": "rich_text",
          "name": "Heading",
          "settings": {
            "content": "<h1>How to Wear Engagement Ring and Wedding Band: A Complete Guide</h1>",
            "custom_id": ""
          }
        },
        "follow_us_3ggfwT": {
          "type": "follow_us",
          "settings": {
            "heading": "Follow Us on"
          }
        },
        "rich_text_8DL9Df": {
          "type": "rich_text",
          "name": "Intro",
          "settings": {
            "content": "<p>Choosing how to wear your engagement and wedding rings is a meaningful decision that reflects tradition, personal style, and symbolism. Whether you're preparing for your wedding day or updating your everyday style, understanding how to wear engagement ring and wedding band helps you showcase your rings beautifully and comfortably. This guide explains traditional and modern ring placement, how eternity rings fit into the stack, and style tips inspired by today’s most-loved jewelry trends.</p><p>Throughout this guide, real customer habits, jewelers’ insights, and timeless etiquette are combined to help you find the perfect way to wear your rings confidently.</p>",
            "custom_id": ""
          }
        },
        "rich_text_aWgRJn": {
          "type": "rich_text",
          "name": "Understanding the Traditional Order of Rings",
          "settings": {
            "content": "<h2>Understanding the Traditional Order of Rings</h2>",
            "custom_id": "understanding"
          }
        },
        "image_MAmRxK": {
          "type": "image",
          "settings": {
            "image": "shopify://shop_images/How_to_Wear_Engagement_Ring_and_Wedding_Band_A_Complete_Guide.png"
          }
        },
        "rich_text_bUfHBT": {
          "type": "rich_text",
          "name": "Understanding the Paragraph",
          "settings": {
            "content": "<h3>Wedding Band Comes First</h3><p>Traditionally, the wedding band is worn closest to the heart meaning it sits at the base of the ring finger, followed by the engagement ring. When selecting an<a href=\"https://www.lucirajewelry.com/collections/engagement-ring\"> <span style=\"text-decoration:underline\">engagement ring</span></a>, many couples choose designs that pair seamlessly with a wedding band for a cohesive, elegant stack.</p><h3>Engagement Ring on Top</h3><p>The engagement ring is typically worn above the wedding band. This order is especially common among brides who want their center stone to be the focal point of the stack.</p>",
            "custom_id": ""
          }
        },
        "rich_text_pW9Jpd": {
          "type": "rich_text",
          "name": "Modern Ways to Wear Your Ring Stack",
          "settings": {
            "content": "<h2>Modern Ways to Wear Your Ring Stack</h2><p>While tradition matters, modern couples are redefining how to wear engagement ring wedding band and eternity ring to suit their personal style.</p>",
            "custom_id": ""
          }
        },
        "image_pMRppG": {
          "type": "image",
          "settings": {
            "image": "shopify://shop_images/Modern_Ways_to_Wear_Your_Ring_Stack.png"
          }
        },
        "rich_text_JmwFBb": {
          "type": "rich_text",
          "name": "Modern Ways to Wear Paragraph",
          "settings": {
            "content": "<h3>Switching the Order</h3><p>Some prefer to wear the engagement ring first, especially if it has a built-in contour or unique shape that looks best at the base of the finger. This style is popular among those choosing an<a href=\"https://www.lucirajewelry.com/collections/engagement-rings-for-women\"> <span style=\"text-decoration:underline\">engagement ring for women</span></a> with distinctive silhouettes.</p><h3>Wearing Rings on Different Hands</h3><p>Many contemporary brides and grooms choose to wear their engagement ring and wedding band on separate hands for comfort or aesthetic balance. This is increasingly common with bold styles such as an<a href=\"https://www.lucirajewelry.com/collections/mens-engagement-rings\"> <span style=\"text-decoration:underline\">engagement ring for men</span></a>.</p>",
            "custom_id": "modern"
          }
        },
        "rich_text_FGe3Vh": {
          "type": "rich_text",
          "name": "How Eternity Rings Fit Into the Stack",
          "settings": {
            "content": "<h2>How Eternity Rings Fit Into the Stack</h2>",
            "custom_id": ""
          }
        },
        "image_4x3btq": {
          "type": "image",
          "settings": {
            "image": "shopify://shop_images/How_Eternity_Rings_Fit_Into_the_Stack.png"
          }
        },
        "rich_text_Jc4E4r": {
          "type": "rich_text",
          "name": "How Eternity Rings Paragraph",
          "settings": {
            "content": "<h3>The Classic Trio</h3><p>When you add an eternity ring typically gifted on anniversaries or major milestones it usually sits above the wedding band and engagement ring. The sparkle encircling the band enhances the overall brilliance of the stack.</p><h3>Alternative Styling</h3><p>Some wear their eternity ring at the base, followed by the wedding band and engagement ring. Others choose to wear the eternity ring on the opposite hand to keep the trio balanced.</p>",
            "custom_id": "how"
          }
        },
        "rich_text_6WCWXy": {
          "type": "rich_text",
          "name": "Cultural and Regional Differences",
          "settings": {
            "content": "<h2>Cultural and Regional Differences</h2><h3>European Traditions</h3><p>In some European countries, the engagement ring is worn on the right hand until the wedding day, then moved to the left hand to pair with the wedding band.</p><h3>American Customs</h3><p>Most couples in the United States follow the wedding-band-first tradition introduced in the Victorian era.</p><h3>Global Modern Styles</h3><p>Globally, modern couples opt for simplicity, minimalism, and individualized placement. Coordinated sets or<a href=\"https://www.lucirajewelry.com/collections/couple-rings\"> <span style=\"text-decoration:underline\"><strong>couple rings</strong></span></a> have become increasingly popular for couples wanting matching symbolism.</p>",
            "custom_id": "cultural"
          }
        },
        "rich_text_xii4nX": {
          "type": "rich_text",
          "name": "Styling Tips for Comfort and Aesthetic Balance",
          "settings": {
            "content": "<h2>Styling Tips for Comfort and Aesthetic Balance</h2><h3>Choose Rings That Stack Smoothly</h3><p>Pairing rings with complementary shapes helps maintain comfort. Flat-edge wedding bands or contoured bands reduce gaps and improve the fit against your engagement ring.</p><h3>Consider Everyday Wear</h3><p>Your ring stack should work for daily activities. If you work actively with your hands, wearing only the wedding band might be more practical at times.</p><h3>Match Metals and Proportions</h3><p>For a cohesive look, match metals like platinum with platinum or gold with gold. You can also create contrast with mixed metals for a modern look.</p>",
            "custom_id": "styling"
          }
        },
        "rich_text_rQKzCe": {
          "type": "rich_text",
          "name": "Final Thoughts",
          "settings": {
            "content": "<h2>Final Thoughts</h2><p>How you choose to wear your engagement and wedding rings is deeply personal. Whether you follow tradition, embrace a modern approach, or create your own stacking style, your rings should feel meaningful and comfortable every day. From traditional band-first styling to personalized combinations with eternity rings, there’s no single “right” way only the way that feels right for you.</p><p>Explore Timeless Ring Designs!</p><p>If you're looking for elegant craftsmanship and beautifully detailed bands, explore <a href=\"https://www.lucirajewelry.com/\"><span style=\"text-decoration:underline\">Lucira Jewelry’s</span></a> collection of modern and classic rings. Find the perfect pieces to celebrate your love story, your way.</p>",
            "custom_id": "final"
          }
        }
      },
